# Badge 徽标

**Category**: react
**URL**: https://www.heroui.com/cn/docs/react/components/badge
**Source**: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/heroui-inc/heroui/refs/heads/v3/apps/docs/content/docs/cn/react/components/(data-display)/badge.mdx
